Speed Magazine - July 2014  PH

140 Pages | True PDF | English | 17 MB 


This July, Speed sees you through a revolution of sound as high-resolution audio shapes the future of digital music. Sit back and devour or create multimedia content on the hottest new devices to hit town, including the Microsoft Surface Pro 3, LG Ultra HD TV, Sony RX100 III, Huawei Ascend P7, HTC One mini 2, Bang & Olufsen speakers, and Audio-Technica, Pioneer, and Bose headphones.
